', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/157096/', '', 'Suvorexant, Flurazepam, Methohexital, Zolpidem, Pentobarbital, Zaleplon, Dichloralphenazone, Valerian, Temazepam, Butabarbital, Secobarbital, More', 'Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Inebilizumab, Cladribine, Belimumab, Sutimlimab, Risankizumab, More', 1767369485);
